file.string: Match T shape to\n create explosive fruit!
Match L shape can also\n create explosive fruit!
Combine 2 special fruit\n to get big explode!
Make matches inside\n Lock to clear it!
Make matches next to\n Cookie to clear it!
Cake will block the pieces!\n Make matches to clear it!
Make matches twice\n to clear Candy!
Clear the pieces below\n to collect Starfish!
Make matches to clear\n sand and collect Shell!
Fruit Generator will\n produce special fruit!
Hammer can clear all the\n pieces in row and column!
Bomb can clear all\n the pieces around it!
Glove can swap two pieces\n without losing moves!
